ns0:svg.ns0:text: Look carefully at the picture showing elements of the weather. Use what you see to answer the following questions. Make sure to think about what you've learned in class about the weather!
1. What are the main things you see in this picture related to the weather?
2. Can you point out and name two things in the picture that help us understand if it's a sunny or rainy day?
3. What do you think the picture is trying to show about the different types of weather?
4. How do the elements shown in the picture affect our daily lives or the way we plan our activities?
5. Imagine you are a weather reporter. Use the elements shown in the picture to create a short weather forecast for tomorrow.
